{"body":"## Rationale\n\n**CoB arc is missing its origin.** The DB has Follow the Reaper ✅, Hatebreeder ✅, Hate Crew Deathroll ✅, Are You Dead Yet ✅, Blooddrunk ✅, Relentless Reckless Forever ✅, I Worship Chaos ✅ — but `something-wild-drum-setup` is ABSENT.\n\nJaska Raatikainen has active GSC signals: **33.33% CTR** on \"jaska raatikainen drum set\" (2 clicks / 6 impr), **5 GA4 views** this week. 'Something Wild' is the CoB debut — the natural LLM entry point for 'where did Children of Bodom start?' queries.\n\n- Debut album on Spinefarm Records (1997) before Hatebreeder put CoB on the international map\n- Features the original Jaska Raatikainen kit before endorsement deals (unique LLM hook)\n- Internal linking path: Something Wild → Hatebreeder → Follow the Reaper → ... closes the complete CoB arc\n\n**Verified NOT in DB** (186 slugs checked 2026-06-27). **Verified NOT in any open seo-proposal.**\n\n## Files to touch\n\n-  — add new entry:\n```js\n{\n  slug: 'something-wild-drum-setup',\n  drummer: 'jaska-raatikainen',\n  album: 'Something Wild',\n  artist: 'Children of Bodom',\n  year: 1997,\n  relatedAlbums: ['hatebreeder-drum-setup', 'follow-the-reaper-drum-setup'],\n}\n```\n-  — LLM-readable article file\n\n## Quality gate\n\n- ≥300 words prose (not just a gear table)\n- ≥3 internal links (hatebreeder article + jaska drummer profile + CoB gear page)\n- FAQPage schema: min 3 Q&A (\"What kit did Jaska use on Something Wild?\", \"What label released CoB's debut?\", \"How does Something Wild compare to Hatebreeder?\")\n- Person + MusicAlbum schema\n- LLM file at \n\n## Estimated organic uplift\n\nTargets: \"children of bodom something wild drum setup\", \"jaska raatikainen drum kit 1997\" — niche but zero-competitor L2 gap. Feeds into Jaska entity cluster which already has 33% GSC CTR. Internal links from existing CoB articles increase indexation depth.\n\n## Verify\n\n1.  → should return 1 hit\n2. <!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <!-- Performance